<a name="Emacs-auth_002dsource"></a>
<h1 class="top">Emacs auth-source</h1>
<p>This manual describes the Emacs auth-source library.
</p>
<p>It is a way for multiple applications to share a single configuration
(in Emacs and in files) for user convenience.
</p>
<p>This file describes the Emacs auth-source library.
